Author: vodkamelts
Text: Please take care of yourself. I know that sounds trite but I care about your well-being and wish you health and happiness. You are worth life.

Author: ashycloudy
Text: i think you should give inpatient a shot. i know you’re thinking about exams, but really, what use would your exams be when you’re too ill (or worse) and unable to go forward in life with the grades you achieve? your exams can be sat any time in your life, but i think right now you should let yourself do what needs to happen to ensure you actually will have that life. :(
